data.description: Welcome to 7220 Canterbury Drive in Pasadena Hills, This 4 Bedroom 2 full Bathroom home has been updated and feels like home as soon as you walk in. Upon entry you will immediately notice the refinished hardwood floors, the open floorplan and the large windows that let in ample natural light. You will be pleasantly surprised with the updated eat in kitchen, large family room and dining room. The main level also features a room that could be used as a home office or another living room. Going upstairs you have 4 large bedrooms and one of the best bathroom renovations of a full bathroom you have ever seen. There is a partially finished basement that has been upgraded with acoustic walls. This also features a newer roof and a huge side lot that is included in this sale.  Make your appointment to see this home today.
